          "number": 6,
          "slidetitle": "Mitigating Third-Party Data Risks",
          "subtitle": "Reducing Exposure to External Data Failures",
          "slidecontent": "• Vetting third-party data providers before integrating their feeds into your platform\n\n• Check for SLAs\n\n• Monitoring live data streams for sudden gaps or anomalies in pricing and availability\n\n• Building fallback options so the platform can display cached or default content during outages\n\n• Regular audits of supplier data quality to catch persistent inaccuracies early\n\n• Training staff to recognise and escalate third-party data failures quickly"
